Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远古时期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让恐惧与绝望瀰漫于世上的传说中的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在与其纯白闪耀的鬣毛一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将甦醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slayers Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judgment 甦醒的白银！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我可要发飙咯！
